HEADWORD: Reefing
<hw>Reef"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Naut.)</fld> <def>The process of
taking in a reef.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Reefing bowsprit</b></col>, <cd>a bowsprit so rigged that
